    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example delivers a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Key preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a reinforced rear subframe carrier and a top-end overhaul with shim-and-bucket valve adjustments. The chassis remains composed on Bilstein B6 dampers, while the M-Variable differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is dialed-in for high-performance driving. A true driver's spec with mechanical integrity at the forefront.",
